        <p class="eyebrow">Commercial Refrigeration — Los Angeles &amp; SoCal</p>
        <h1><span class="brand-name">Delfield</span> Commercial Refrigeration Repair in Los Angeles</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">Expert service for Delfield N-series reach-ins, refrigerated prep tables, mega tops, drop-in cold pans, salad bar units, and ingredient bins throughout Los Angeles, Orange County, and Southern California. Institutional specialists.</p>
