      <ul class="scb-list">
        <li>✓ $120 Commercial Diagnostic → Applied</li>
        <li>✓ HACCP Compliance Documentation</li>
        <li>✓ Drop-In Cold Pan Specialists</li>
        <li>✓ EPA 608 Certified</li>
        <li>✓ ITW / OEM Parts Access</li>
        <li>✓ Institutional PM Contracts</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="scb-note">Pan rail above 41°F? That's a HACCP CCP event. Call immediately — we dispatch same-day.</p>
